    public class EnumLongConverter<E extends Enum<E>>
extends com.blockwithme.util.shared.converters.LongConverterBase<Object,E>
implements com.blockwithme.util.shared.converters.ConfiguredConverter<Object,E>
    EnumLongConverter implements a LongConverter for some enum type. It is assumed that all enum constant names can be converted to unique Base40 long.
